/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9750efba0247ec3a691186ebbfcb2e762c59708d","tid":778301,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T23:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f39ccb8d2d7bf77277ba1fd5d9822cf4457b90","tid":778301,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:28:48.000Z","msg":"精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992285268a62a0da0658009d4c3d61d6981d3185","tid":778301,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:44:12.000Z","msg":"推到689仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b560375a9e7be396cd1a5743324cae981586d34","tid":778301,"uid":153972,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99293437976d995ebcb8317655d86d2cdd4ecc9a","tid":778301,"uid":57185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T17:58:59.000Z","msg":"件事係點做到？係夾定曬時間？<br />\n好複雜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"2011年UGL畀錢梁振英時，Juan Santamaria根本同UGL冇交集，而且嗰時UGL同禮頓係兩間獨立上市公司，CIMIC(禮頓)係2016年尾先收購UGL<br />\n<br />\n上面圖講嘅Juan Santamaria，我查Bloomberg佢嘅簡歷:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=316512166&amp;ticker=CIM:AU&amp;previousCapId=9170934&amp;previousTitle=CPB%20Contractors%20Pty%20Limited\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fresearch%2Fstocks%2Fpeople%2Fperson.asp%3FpersonId%3D316512166%26ticker%3DCIM%3AAU%26previousCapId%3D9170934%26previousTitle%3DCPB%2520Contractors%2520Pty%2520Limited&d=baXN5%2FMIYVOlq4sSqcn12QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=019b391f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=316512166&amp;ticker=CIM:AU&amp;previousCapId=9170934&amp;previousTitle=CPB%20Contractors%20Pty%20Limited</a><br />\n2005至2012: Chief Executive Officer and Chief Operating Officer of ACS Infrastructure in United States and Canada<br />\n2012至2017-1-12: Executive General Manager of Public Private Partnerships (PPPs) and Construction West for Leighton Contractors Pty Limited<br />\n2017-1-25至2017-8-31: Managing Director of UGL Limited<br />\n2017-8-31-現在 : Managing Director of CPB Contractors Pty Limited<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，2011年西班牙ACS集團增持德國建築公司Hochtief股權至超過五成:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dw.com/en/spains-acs-takes-majority-stake-in-hochtief/a-15170633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fspains-acs-takes-majority-stake-in-hochtief%2Fa-15170633&d=baXN5%2FMIYVOlq4sSqcn12QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=90f8cd05\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dw.com/en/spains-acs-takes-majority-stake-in-hochtief/a-15170633</a><br />\n<br />\n而Hochtief原本係禮頓控股絕對大股東:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hochtief.com/hochtief_en/pdfservice/6867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hochtief.com%2Fhochtief_en%2Fpdfservice%2F6867&d=baXN5%2FMIYVOlq4sSqcn12QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=edcc93ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hochtief.com/hochtief_en/pdfservice/6867</a><br />\n<br />\nSantamaria先生 2012年由西班牙ACS北美公司轉到禮頓<br />\n<br />\n2015年禮頓控股改名為CIMIC集團:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smh.com.au/business/leighton-to-change-name-to-cimic-in-wake-of-corruption-allegations-20150320-1m40j3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Fbusiness%2Fleighton-to-change-name-to-cimic-in-wake-of-corruption-allegations-20150320-1m40j3.html&d=baXN5%2FMIYVOlq4sSqcn12QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=511d2eac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.smh.com.au/business/leighton-to-change-name-to-cimic-in-wake-of-corruption-allegations-20150320-1m40j3.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2016年10月10日先至提出收購澳洲上市公司UGL，同日於公開市場買入14% UGL股票:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.afr.com/street-talk/corporate-buyer-snaps-up-14pc-ug